---
id: "JRN_SpecCleanup"
title: Documentation Integrity Maintenance
description: Manual or automated cleanup of documentation categories.
trigger: User removes a documentation category via CLI.
outcome: Documentation is cleaned up safely without breaking dependencies.
requirements: REQ_Discovery
---

sequenceDiagram
    participant PER_SystemAnalyst as System Analyst
    participant COMP_CLI as FoundrySpec CLI
    
    PER_SystemAnalyst->>COMP_CLI: foundryspec remove <category>
    COMP_CLI->>COMP_CLI: Scan for dependencies
    alt Has Dependencies
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_SystemAnalyst: Error: blocked
    else Safe
        COMP_CLI->>COMP_CLI: Delete directory
        COMP_CLI->>COMP_CLI: Remove rule
        COMP_CLI-->>PER_SystemAnalyst: Success
    end
